Samsung has launched the first 'next generation' virtual reality headset. 

Called the Samsung Gear VR, users slip a Note 3 tablet into the $200 headset to provide the screen.

It was developed with Oculus, the VR firm recently bought by Facebook, and complete complete with games and VR movie viewing software. 

